name: OLIVIA DUFF
body:
### Welcome to my GitHub.
I'm a recent graduate of Georgetown University passionate about the intersection of art and technology. I studied Theater and Performance Studies and received a minor in Computer Science. I hope to use my design skills and technical abilities to create tools that are at once functional and beautiful. 

### Why me?
I'm passionate about clean, elegant, and intuitive design. I'm highly motivated, curious, and detail oriented. 

###Interests
* UI/UX Design
* Web Development
* Mobile App Development 
* Human-Computer Interaction
* Software Engineering
* Graphic Design
